# Post-Edit Verification

`AGENTS.md` is the workflow source of truth.

After substantive edits, run `npm run verify` and fix any failures before finishing. Keep `src/routeTree.gen.ts` generated, and add `// @vitest-environment jsdom` only when a test genuinely needs DOM APIs.
